Posted By: Max Weder
Gypsy Queen Dailey for trade (at this point).  Before it gets slabbed and off to auction, I thought I'd post Dailey here, asking for trade for my usual assortment of baseball books, cards and ephemera that no one else seems to collect here but no one seems to have.

Here's Dailey

[IMG]http://farm1.static.flickr.com/108/274258073_9e95c7690d.jpg[/IMG]

Trade I'm looking for?

Baseball books --old and interesting, especially older dust jackets

See my want list at [url]http://www.network54.com/Forum/376270/thread/1167428662/last-1167446705/Wanted+Baseball+Books+--+Will+trade+baseball+cards+for+books[/url]

As well, I am always looking for Northwest Coast/Western Canadian cards and ephemera:

Obaks:  Ten Million
Vancouver or Victoria T4
Vancouver Senior Amateur League Cards
Capilano popcorn cards

old programs, photos or other ephemera of Vancouver or other points in Western Canada

Thanks,

Max

Posted By: barrysloate
Max- I still have a few books left- I'm not sure I want to go too deep into my few rare ones but perhaps I could offer some nice ones not necessarily on your list. If you want to kick it around, let me know at bsloate@att.net      Barry
